User :
Navigate to the Users Setup Page
Go to Setup.
Under Administration, click Users.
Select New User.
Fill in User Details:
Last Name: Consultant.
User License: Salesforce Platform.
Profile: Standard Platform User.
Save the new user.
Configure the Approver Settings
Navigate to the User Settings Page:
Go to Setup.
Under Administration, select Users.
Select Mani  in the user list, then click Edit next to it.
Set Approver Settings:
Scroll down to the bottom of the page to locate the Approver Settings section.
In the Manager field, select Consultant from the list.
Save the changes occured.
